reviewText:
Very fast shipping. Excellent customer service.
My son enjoy watching all this videos. It is  a good video to discuss and reflex with your children about good and bad.
My daughters love (5 and 3) this movie.
Accurate and good story of how St. Francis turned his life over to Jesus. Kids loved it.
One of my favorites growing up, now my kids love it!
Purchased this for our four year old. She loves it. It is an enjoyable tale about Saint Francis - edifying and without any vulgarity.

A wonderful story, well written, nicely illustrated, good for both kids and adults.  There is a wonderful message in the story for all of us to be aware of.  My wife's CCD class learned much about this saint for out time.
